canonical:
  title: 偶書
  author: 鄭希良
  language: lzh
  text: 年來索寞鴨江濱回首塵沙欲問津客裏偶逢寒食雨夢中猶憶故園春一生愁病添衰鬢萬里溪山著放臣直以踈慵成落魄非關時命滯詩人
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 偶書
  author: 鄭希良
  language: lzh
  text: 年來索寞鴨江濱。回首塵沙欲問津。客裏偶逢寒食雨。夢中猶憶故園春。一生愁病添衰鬢。萬里溪山著放臣。直以踈慵成落魄。非關時命滯詩人。
korean:
  title: 우서
  author: 정희량
  language: kor
  text: |-
    여러 해 전부터 압록강 가에서 삭막하게 지내다가
    진사에서 머리 돌려 나루터를 물으려 하네
    객지에서 우연히 한식의 비를 만나
    꿈속에서 아직도 고향의 봄을 기억하네
    일생의 시름과 병은 흰 살쩍을 보태었는데
    만리의 시내와 산은 쫓겨난 신하를 붙여 주네
    바로 등한하고 게으름으로 낙백하게 되었거니
    운명이 시인을 곤궁하게 한 것이 아닐러라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1440_010_0470&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 낙백(落魄) : '
    value: 곤궁한 생활로 직업이 없다는 말이다.
english:
  title: Casual Writing
  author: Jeong Hee-ryang
  language: eng
  text: |-
    For years now I have dwelt in desolation by the Yalu's shore,
    Turning back through dust and sand, seeking passage across the ford.
    By chance I meet the Cold Food rains in this foreign land,
    Yet in dreams I still remember the spring of my native garden.

    A lifetime of sorrow and illness has whitened my temples,
    Yet ten thousand miles of streams and mountains shelter this banished minister.
    It is my own neglect and sloth that have brought me to ruin—
    Not fate's decree that has reduced a poet to such straits.
  footnotes:
    - The "Cold Food" festival (寒食) is a traditional observance occurring a few days before the Qingming Festival, traditionally a time when exiles and travelers would feel their displacement most keenly.
    - The speaker identifies himself as a "banished minister" (放臣), suggesting this poem was written during a period of political exile or dismissal from office.
